{"tid":1829686,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【都市日報】裁員又拖糧。","createTime":"2020-01-19T03:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T05:20:44.000Z","uid":202464,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e99350b7689587627520ae629b41bc1d185c48f4","tid":1829686,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T03:45:33.000Z","msg":"去年因財困賣盤，已暫停派發的《都市日報》傳出拖糧傳聞。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，《都市》去年底因應賣盤先後採取多輪裁員行動，去年12月公司主席李永康對外發通告，宣稱由12月13日起提前放聖誕假，實質進行另一波裁員，進一步遣散數十名員工。<br />\n<br />\n受影響員工離職後卻疑遭拖糧，未能如期收到上月的工資及銷售佣金，單計受影響的營銷部門員工，遭拖欠的款項累計已近100萬元。"},{"pid":"2dbb4b0cf651b2f3fcfbadaa4cab7b842f6a8a78","tid":1829686,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T03:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />員工慘"},{"pid":"e3b21e7a59e6383bf56f4a6f10394a64a7cf7943","tid":1829686,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:25:39.000Z","msg":"想知其他免費報點樣？"},{"pid":"99d74e7a7fc032f04257abf1d9f383b94c6a06a4","tid":1829686,"uid":144541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:38:31.000Z","msg":"唔怪得冇哂影<br />\n<br />\n今日中環見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3be2ea25683fa9f909d99d1883c7137611edec2","tid":1829686,"uid":34184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:41:06.000Z","msg":"wrong hole?"},{"pid":"11ba10414fb425408235d956a10581d251058dd5","tid":1829686,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:42:37.000Z","msg":"仲係wrong hole 做老細？"},{"pid":"0a9b0ed63114d4deda699bdb8a874ce2942ffe98","tid":1829686,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:42:38.000Z","msg":"唔好又比紅色資本收編呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5fe5335c63a50b825f22db7a11860f4ee62fc0","tid":1829686,"uid":12331,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0a9b0ed63114d4deda699bdb8a874